<TMPL_UNLESS NAME='package'>

This template lists information about a Debian package.  It requires the
following parameters:

[[table header="no" data="""
package|The package name.
version|The package version.
section|The section the package belongs in, e.g. editors, graphics,
non-free/mail.
architecture|The architecture(s) the package can be built for.
depends|Other packages this package depends on.
recommends (optional)|Other packages this package recommends.
suggests (optional)|Other packages this package suggests.
description_short|The first line of the package's description.
description_long|The remainder of the package's description.
homepage (optional)|A URL where the package's original source can be found.
tarball (optional)|Original source tarball.
deb (optional)|A binary .deb.
diff|The diff that is applied to the source tarball before building the binary .deb.
"""]]

<TMPL_ELSE>

#### <a name="<TMPL_VAR NAME='package'>"></a> <TMPL_VAR NAME='package'> ####

<table class="package">
<tr>
<td> Version </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='version'> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td> Section </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='section'> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td> Architecture </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='architecture'> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td> Depends </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='depends'> </td>
</tr>
<TMPL_IF NAME='recommends'>
<tr>
<td> Recommends </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='recommends'> </td>
</tr>
</TMPL_IF>
<TMPL_IF NAME='suggests'>
<tr>
<td> Suggests </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='suggests'> </td>
</tr>
</TMPL_IF>
<tr>
<td> Description </td>
<td> <TMPL_VAR NAME='description_short'>
<TMPL_VAR NAME='description_long'>
</td>
</tr>
<TMPL_IF NAME='homepage'>
<tr>
<td> Homepage </td>
<td> <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_homepage'>"><TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_homepage'></a> </td>
</tr>
</TMPL_IF>
<TMPL_IF NAME='tarball'>
<tr>
<td> Source </td>
<td> <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_tarball'>"><TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_tarball'></a> </td>
</tr>
</TMPL_IF>
<TMPL_IF NAME='diff'>
<tr>
<td> Diff </td>
<td> <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_diff'>"><TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_diff'></a> </td>
</tr>
</TMPL_IF>
<TMPL_IF NAME='deb'>
<tr>
<td> Package </td>
<td> <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_deb'>"><TMPL_VAR NAME='raw_deb'></a> </td>
</tr>
</TMPL_IF>
</table>
</TMPL_UNLESS>
